lá atrás.

517
00:47:17,703 --> 00:47:19,248
São avisos.

518
00:47:19,745 --> 00:47:22,284
As tribos talharam
antes de fugirem.

519
00:47:22,938 --> 00:47:24,402
- Fugiram?
- Eles sabiam...

520
